{"tid":396260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"致讀DGS背後的傻仔","createTime":"2017-09-11T14:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T20:21:54.000Z","uid":146263,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"47ad24936d80df3adde14cca4613c77bb85e5ce6","tid":396260,"uid":146263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">「遠在我的眼前，近在我的心」</div><br />\n  你既離開太突然，我想回應你都回唔切，所以我想係到同你講，雖然唔知你會唔會睇到。<br />\n<br />\n  首先，我冇嬲你，亦都明白你點解要離開，雖然我地認識左係一段好短既日子，但你係我心入面已經佔左一個好重要既位置。 <br />\n  你既出現不但無對我做成麻煩，反而令我既生活多左一份色彩，每一日可以陪你起身，陪你訓教，陪你傾計，對我來講已經係一種幸福。    <br />\n<br />\n   茫茫人海之中我地能夠相遇是緣，能夠相識是份，能夠相愛是情。<br />\n   你話過下年完DSE既時候，叫我搵返你。我一定會搵返你，我會等你，如果你到時還記得我。<br />\n<br />\n  古有楊過苦等16年，今有小毒撚苦等７個月。"},{"pid":"377a20081c771b3fed030ac927b3f47b31a6a2ac","tid":396260,"uid":21423,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:02:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"80686ff0d2eb37b0f948c414ffd73e91c27f24d5","tid":396260,"uid":41432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T14:04:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DGS女校嚟，點會有傻仔？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd76cbfd8ccdd5f7432f5a2ca168eb680d3fade0","tid":396260,"uid":126836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-11T15:18:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>DGS女校嚟，點會有傻仔？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c01be8360d36d8d034b76a1a5765f1f19fb53fe","tid":396260,"uid":146263,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T03:02:51.000Z","msg":"每日一推"},{"pid":"0dcf0e10257f8d11de8d49811879eaae741f6ce5","tid":396260,"uid":146263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T07:56:44.000Z","msg":"一推再推 推到下年"},{"pid":"50252361f16b1d2730c22944cec82edfe7655f3e","tid":396260,"uid":24596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-13T12:37:28.000Z","msg":"